w that both the contraction rebound event and the\nsubsequent pulsation behavior follow analytically from an analysis of the new\nidentities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Mar 2023 16:53:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-03"}
