nt of any particular asteroid morphology, and all shed\nparticles enter the same evolutionary path. We also find that the orbital\nenergy of the particle cloud is statistically independent of the surface\ncontact property, meaning that the collision coefficient of restitution is a\nnonsensitive parameter in the outward spreading process of the shed particles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Apr 2023 02:30:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
